title: Does Your Education Suck?
itunes:title: Does Your Education Suck?
description:
Episode 129 - Education is probably the #1 determining factor of you success. Don't get me wrong, I don't mean traditional schooling, I mean self education. Educating yourself has never been easier or cheaper and in this episode I let you in on how to get a great education for a small price or even free!
